1
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:09,600
Early this morning,

2
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,120
someone in a secluded alley

3
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:12,800
found Bao's wife's body.

4
00:01:15,720 --> 00:01:16,640
Bao's wife?

5
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,360
Wasn't she in the hospital?

6
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,600
Why would she go to a secluded place?

7
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:22,960
Uncle Qin,

8
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,640
didn't you say before

9
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,960
that Lord Guan's opera costume was missing?

10
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:26,960
But why

11
00:01:27,960 --> 00:01:28,800
last night

12
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:30,920
did Boss Mei wear it on stage?

13
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,240
Where did you find it?

14
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,400
I don't know what happened either.

15
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,040
I was wondering about that too.

16
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,680
After returning from the Police Department last time,

17
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,000
it was placed perfectly back in the trunk.

18
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:43,960
However,

19
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:44,640
the way

20
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,560
the clothes were folded

21
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,680
was clearly different from how I usually do it.

22
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,320
It looks like someone put it back.

23
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,360
Then take out this Theatrical Attire

24
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,760
and let us take a look.

25
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,080
Okay.

26
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,280
Er Yixiang,

27
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,760
take out Lord Guan's

28
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,400
Theatrical Attire

29
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,400
and show it to the inspectors.

30
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:03,520
Boss Mei,

31
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,240
please give me the key.

32
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,400
Inspector Huang,

33
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,040
about that Theatrical Attire...

34
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,760
It was originally kept backstage.

35
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:25,480
Ever since

36
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:27,320
Yuejiao and Brother Bao died,

37
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,040
everyone has been saying

38
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:31,040
that Lord Guan manifested to kill them.

39
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:32,760
My heart

40
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:33,960
has been uneasy all along.

41
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,200
So,

42
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,920
I took that Theatrical Attire

43
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,400
and put it in the cabinet in my room.

44
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,560
It's human blood!

45
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,280
It's human blood!

46
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,120
Don't talk nonsense!

47
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,120
It's human blood!

48
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:54,920
Boss Mei,

49
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,120
why is there blood on your opera costume?

50
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,400
Where did you go last night?

51
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,960
Where did this blood come from?

52
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,560
Last night...

53
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,480
I don't know either!

54
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,200
After the show ended,

55
00:03:09,320 --> 00:03:10,680
I took off the opera costume

56
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,880
and went back to my room.

57
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,040
I have no idea why

58
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,240
there is blood on that opera costume!

59
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:16,760
Inspector Huang,

60
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:18,760
I can prove it.

61
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,640
From last night until now,

62
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:21,480
Boss Mei

63
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,040
has never left the opera house!

64
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:24,360
Yes, Inspector Huang.

65
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:25,720
There must be some misunderstanding.

66
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,480
Boss Mei couldn't be the killer.

67
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,520
That's right.

68
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,160
Did I say Boss Mei is the killer?

69
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,200
Boss Mei,

70
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,800
I need to take this Theatrical Attire

71
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,760
back to the Police Department.

72
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,440
I also ask Boss Mei

73
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,000
and everyone here

74
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,320
to cooperate with the investigation.

75
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,000
Stay in the opera house for now

76
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,080
and do not leave without permission

77
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,760
until we find the real

78
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:49,320
killer.

79
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:50,160
In addition,

80
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,240
I also need to take

81
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:52,920
this Guandao from the Shrine Room

82
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,640
with me for investigation.

83
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,080
Xiao Yuejiao

84
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:07,600
did indeed want to

85
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,160
take the opera house back from Mei Yanhong.

86
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,000
That's why

87
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,320
she poisoned her teacup,

88
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,080
but Brother Bao drank it by mistake.

89
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,720
Then, this Xiao Yuejiao

90
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,080
was found

91
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:21,760
brutally murdered in her own room.

92
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,240
But

93
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,200
Auntie Wang clearly confessed

94
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,240
that she was

95
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,760
the one who killed Xiao Yuejiao.

96
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,480
However, she couldn't explain

97
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,880
where the broadsword

98
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,480
that actually killed Xiao Yuejiao

99
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,360
came from.

100
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:35,320
Even if it was caused by a Guandao,

101
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:36,760
Auntie Wang is an old woman.

102
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,320
How could she possibly lift it?

103
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,640
I found that

104
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,480
the victim had two wounds on her body.

105
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,320
One was caused by a kitchen knife,

106
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:46,240
and the other,

107
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,440
on the artery of her neck,

108
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,080
was caused by a broadsword.

109
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,480
That was the fatal wound.

110
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,640
To kill one person,

111
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:57,080
why use two murder weapons?

112
00:04:58,920 --> 00:04:59,720
What if

113
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,800
there were two killers?

114
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,640
No wonder

115
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:07,320
when Xiao Yuejiao died,

116
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,640
you said there were two killers.

117
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,760
You had figured it out all along.

118
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,720
Didn't you already ask Chun Cheng

119
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,880
to take that Guandao

120
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:17,520
to compare it with the wounds

121
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,920
on Xiao Yuejiao and Brother Bao's

122
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:19,760
dead bodies?

123
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,200
Whether it's the murder weapon or not,

124
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,040
we'll know in a moment.

125
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,560
But tell me,

126
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,760
who exactly is the killer?

127
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,880
I heard from Chun Cheng

128
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,240
that the cut on Brother Bao's body

129
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,200
was extremely deep.

130
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,000
Obviously, the killer hated him deeply.

131
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,560
Then,

132
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,440
who could simultaneously

133
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,680
hate both Xiao Yuejiao and Brother Bao,

134
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,240
and also have such great strength?

135
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:49,440
So later, Uncle Qin told me

136
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,000
that Xiao Yuejiao had returned.

137
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,120
I went to the opera house,

138
00:05:52,440 --> 00:05:53,360
waited until night,

139
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,880
and killed her.

140
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:55,680
I'll kill you!

141
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,680
Pay for my husband's life!

142
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,000
I'll kill you!

143
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,560
Uncle Qin,

144
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,440
give some money to Bao's wife.

145
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,560
Inspector!

146
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,440
I'll kill you!

147
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,320
Uncle Qin!

148
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:16,920
Who did you say?

149
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,440
Uncle Qin.

150
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:22,120
Watch out!

151
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:25,880
The Guandao and the wounds on Xiao Yuejiao

152
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,200
and Brother Bao's bodies

153
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,240
match perfectly in shape

154
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,000
and length.

155
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:29,800
They are exactly the same.

156
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,040
We can now conclude

157
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,240
that the Guandao in Hongfu Opera House

158
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,880
is the murder weapon

159
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:35,480
that killed the two victims.

160
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:37,440
Perfect timing,

161
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,200
we've also found the killer.

162
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:50,920
Inspector!

163
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,480
Inspector, why are you here?

164
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,240
Where are Uncle Qin and Boss Mei?

165
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,240
Uncle Qin and Boss Mei are in the Shrine Room.

166
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,560
That's Boss Mei's voice!

167
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,360
Mei Yanhong!

168
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,000
Put the knife down!

169
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,560
Darn you!

170
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,120
No!

171
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,640
Xiao Yuejiao,

172
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,240
I killed her.

173
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,480
Why did you kill her?

174
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,000
Because

175
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,440
she wanted to destroy me in the first place.

176
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,640
Yes,

177
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,440
she was quite submissive to me on the surface,

178
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:56,000
but secretly,

179
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:59,640
she tried to poison me time and time again.

180
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,120
How could I tolerate her?

181
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,440
What about Brother Bao?

182
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,000
He was even more darn it.

183
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,440
When he failed

184
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,880
to blackmail me,

185
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,680
he tried to rape me.

186
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:14,000
I threatened him with my own life,

187
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,240
and only then did he leave.

188
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,320
I had put up with him for a very, very long time.

189
00:08:18,800 --> 00:08:19,320
So I

190
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,120
followed him all the way,

191
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,760
until I saw him

192
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,560
walk into a deserted alley,

193
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,360
and then I made my move and killed him.

194
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,240
And then there's

195
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,240
Bao's wife.

196
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,320
She also insulted me time and time again,

197
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,320
and even threatened to kill me in the street.

198
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,760
I had no other choice.

199
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:42,440
I had to strike first.

200
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:44,000
That's how it is.

201
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:46,800
All of them

202
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,880
were killed by me.

203
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:51,800
What about Uncle Qin?

204
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,560
He was always so good to you.

205
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,440
Why did you kill him?

206
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,040
Because he knew I was the killer.

207
00:09:04,800 --> 00:09:05,360
He also said

208
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:07,360
he was going to report me to you.

209
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,440
I had no choice.

210
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,200
Have you guys heard?

211
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,200
That case about Mei Yanhong killing people in the theater.

212
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,880
It's absolutely appalling!

213
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,680
I heard

214
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,920
the authorities have already closed the case.

215
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,360
I also heard

216
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:28,360
that after the Autumn Executions,

217
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,440
she's going to be executed.

218
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,560
I guess that's karma for you.

219
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:32,880
Yeah, yeah.

220
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,560
Seeing her energy on stage normally,

221
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,120
every movement she made

222
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,000
was full of charm.

223
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:38,080
Who would have thought

224
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,760
she was actually such a ruthless character?

225
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:40,720
If you ask me,

226
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,760
people like her should be hacked to pieces.

227
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,760
How dare she murder people so blatantly!

228
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,720
Is there no law anymore?

229
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:46,840
Exactly, exactly!

230
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,480
And to think we used to support her shows so much.

231
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:50,280
You can know a face, but not a heart.

232
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,480
Exactly.

233
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,000
I really didn't expect

234
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,520
Mei Yanhong to be the killer.

235
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,720
Yeah.

236
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,000
Boss Mei,

237
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,960
since she has already confessed,

238
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,400
it seems this case

239
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:09,480
is already case closed.

240
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:13,120
Who would have thought

241
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:15,000
that normally on stage,

242
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,480
the infinitely glamorous Boss Mei

243
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,880
would actually do such a thing?

244
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,000
Boss Mei is not the killer.
